context:
  include:
    - CODEBASE_DOCUMENTATION.md
    - PROGRESS_SUMMARY.md
    - frontend/
    - backend/
    - docs/
  auto_refresh: true

rules:
  - Always adhere to CODEBASE_DOCUMENTATION.md architecture.
  - Write clean, typed (TypeScript) and modular code.
  - Comment all logic clearly.
  - Mirror backend APIs with frontend services under /frontend/services/.
  - Summarize all commits in PROGRESS_SUMMARY.md.
  - Never change structure unless instructed.
  - Follow minimalist, Apple-inspired UI design.
  - Use consistent environment variable management (.env.local / .env.production).
  - Always use TypeScript with strict mode enabled.
  - Implement proper error handling and validation.
  - Use Zod for runtime type validation.
  - Follow RESTful API conventions.
  - Keep components small and focused.
  - Use custom hooks for reusable logic.
  - Document all API endpoints.
  - Write self-documenting code with clear variable names.

